Name: Blobby Jump
About the game: Play as Blobby and jump through 25 progressively difficult and enjoyable levels! After you collect enough coins, you can hone your skills and beat your high score in Infinite Mode! Features: - Different platforms to challenge you in your journey - Collect coins to reach new levels - 25 fun filled levels - Endless fun in Infinite Mode Happy Jumping!
